Question.Subject: how do i get the printer icon back on my internet explorer?
Question.Content:
i reinstalled internet explorer due to a bug, but now my printer icon is gone from the top right corner. how do i get it back?
http://internet-explorer.brothersoft.com/screenshots/Internet-Explorer_1.png that is what im talking about
Question.ChosenAnswer:
Go here: http://support.microsoft.com/kb/923737
Click fix it for me to reset IE to default, should put the printer icon back in the bar.
